txt.en:
A crude note is pinned to the board, scrawled in a red ink and barely legible. You think it says:

'Need more rats!'

You assume that Viznak would like someone to capture more tree-rats for him.
Sneaky tree-rats can be found in the limbs of trees in Agarnaith.\n\nYou should catch some sneaky tree-rats for Viznak.
Viznak has requested an adventurer to capture more of those pesky tree-rats that inhabit the swamps.
